Boris Johnson is consitently more positive than Keir Starmer. But this is really to be expected. In some ways Boris Johnson uses twitter in a different manner to Keir Starmer. Boris generally uses it in the context of his position in the Government, reporting the actions of his Government and painting those actions in a positive light. Keir Starmer on the other hand is spending his time trying to convince people that the Government is doing a bad job at running a country and that people should vote Labour in the next election.
